videos.description: President Barack Obama is with Masai Ujiri at Scotiabank Arena for Game 2.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Obama in Toronto for Game 2 ) 2019// ESHEET

videos.headline: Obama in Toronto for Game 2

videos.description: President Barack Obama and Drake shake hands before the Toronto Raptors take on the Golden State Warriors in Game 2.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Misc. (Obama and Drake meet before Game 2) 2019/06/02

videos.headline: Obama and Drake meet before Game 2

videos.description: Doris Burke says Steph Curry was not healthy the whole game which makes his performance even more impressive.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Doris Burke: Steph was not right the whole game) 2019/06/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Doris Burke: Steph was not right the whole game

videos.description: Stephen A. Smith tells Scott Van Pelt that DeMarcus Cousins was "absolutely phenomenal" in the Warriors' Game 2 victory.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Stephen A.: ‘Cousins was the MVP of the game’) 2019/6/2 ESHEET SVP

videos.headline: Stephen A.: 'Cousins was the MVP of the game'

videos.description: Draymond Green shares an inside joke on bad catchers on the Warriors, but gives Shaun Livingston credit for his catch on the assist to Iguodala.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Draymond: Livingston went from ‘bad receiver’ to ‘Megatron’) 2019/06/02

videos.headline: Draymond: Livingston went from 'bad receiver' to 'Megatron'

videos.description: DeMarcus Cousins joins Scott Van Pelt and says he isn't scared of any moment in the NBA Finals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Cousins: I’m not scared of any moment) 2019/06/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cousins: I'm not scared of any moment

videos.description: Rachel Nichols tells Scott Van Pelt that Andre Iguodala was limping after Game 2 and Klay Thompson expects to play in Game 3 despite his hamstring injury.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Nichols: Iguodala ‘significantly limping’ in locker room) 2019/6/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nichols: Iguodala 'significantly limping' in locker room

videos.description: Brian Windhorst had a unique view from the tunnel during Game 2, and he was able to see how the Warriors' training staff handled Steph Curry's illness, Klay Thompson's injury and more.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Windy says Game 2 was a game for Warriors’ training staff) 2019/6/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Windy says Game 2 was a game for Warriors' training staff

videos.description: Marc Spears and Jerry Bembry invite Chris Herring of FiveThirtyEight to discuss why this is the most exciting NBA Finals in a while after only the first two games.
videos.headline: Suspense in the NBA Finals increases after Game 2

videos.description: In the final moments of Game 2, Shaun Livingston made a crucial play on Steph Curry's pass and found a wide open Andre Iguodala for the dagger 3.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (The anatomy of Iguodala’s Game 2 dagger) 2019/06/03 ESHEET SCEU

videos.headline: The anatomy of Iguodala's Game 2 dagger
